financed him.

69
00:10:47,063 --> 00:10:51,693
You saying he smooth-talked Markham
out of $100,000?

70
00:10:51,985 --> 00:10:53,278
Yep. Me.

71
00:10:54,446 --> 00:10:56,073
- You?
- Me.

72
00:10:57,156 --> 00:11:01,537
- I think I underrated you.
- I think you did, Joe.

73
