I suggest $5,000 apiece
to the war chest.

206
00:25:37,538 --> 00:25:41,457
- $5,000? I could buy a mountain--
- Gentlemen.

207
00:25:43,709 --> 00:25:45,295
Gentlemen!

208
00:25:46,505 --> 00:25:50,175
We wanted an open town
and we got it with Zack Thomas.

209
